> I ran `brew update` and `brew upgrade` where Homebrew noticed that the cleanup hasn't been run in the last 30 days, so it started the cleanup and quits with the error message:

Can you supply the full output of `brew cleanup`? Thanks!

also getting `Error: Permission denied @ apply2files - /usr/local/lib/prey/versions/1.9.9/.DS_Store` during brew install and brew cleanup.

`brew cleanup --debug` gives:

What to do?

Try updating your Homebrew - The update from Friday last week, fixed the issue for me.

```
#: brew update && brew cleanup
```
I actually just did, before receiving that error.

Can you please run the following command and post the output?

```
#: brew config
```
